Use the customer health context below to produce a comprehensive customer analysis.

Customer:
- Name: {{.Customer.Name}}
- Email: {{.Customer.Email}}
- Company: {{.Customer.CompanyName}}
- Source: {{.Customer.Source}}
- MRR: {{formatMoney .Customer.MRRCents .Customer.Currency}}
- Tenure: {{formatTenure .Customer.Tenure}}

Health:
- Overall score: {{.HealthScore.OverallScore}}
- Risk level: {{.HealthScore.RiskLevel}}
- Score change, 7d: {{formatSignedInt .HealthScore.ScoreChange7d}}
- Score change, 30d: {{formatSignedInt .HealthScore.ScoreChange30d}}

Score factors:
{{- range .HealthScore.Factors}}
- {{.Name}}: {{formatFloat .Score}} ({{.Explanation}})
{{- end}}

Recent events:
{{- range .Events}}
- {{.Type}} from {{.Source}}, {{.AgeDays}} days ago: {{.Summary}}
{{- end}}

Return only valid JSON matching this schema:
{
  "insight_type": "customer_analysis",
  "summary": "2-4 sentence customer health analysis",
  "risk_level": "green|yellow|red",
  "confidence": "high|medium|low",
  "signals": [{"name":"signal name","evidence":"specific evidence","impact":"positive|negative|neutral"}],
  "recommendations": [{"action":"specific action","owner":"customer_success|sales|support|billing","priority":"high|medium|low","rationale":"why this action helps"}]
}
